{"id": "1413618581350125701", "channel_id": "1413592330304356402", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "also dunno about getting ovash, like he is alright, not terrible. his thing is getting you low on hp which can be used if you have units that fill your blood furnace really fast but if you dont got that, then his gimmick might kill you rather then help you", "timestamp": "2025-09-05T20:15:33.557000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1413592330304356402", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Help with team building", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1413618780810248282", "channel_id": "1413592330304356402", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "also, for standart banner, I recon you pull for blue and not ultra cus ultra sucks, general consensus is that ultra is the worst of the realms overall especially in standart banner", "timestamp": "2025-09-05T20:16:21.112000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1413592330304356402", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Help with team building", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1413621630499819641", "channel_id": "1413592330304356402", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@606955103601295381> This person doesn't know what they are talking about. \n\nUltra is actually the best realm endgame. The supports are by far the strongest.\n\nUltra does require thinking. Blue does not. Blue is actually the weakest realm in the game and is carried by other realm units (24 is one).\n\nDaffodil is really strong, but requires choosing cards well. This is one of the strongest teams in the endgame. It outperforms every other team in certain stages.", "timestamp": "2025-09-05T20:27:40.531000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["606955103601295381"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1413621630202282046", "filename": "Untitled.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 5682171, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1413592330304356402/1413621630202282046/Untitled.png?ex=69ccd6fc&is=69cb857c&hm=1da3dfbaa502e6b2c36135e1635a664ff97c38c5a8c6f1c7e948e0492f092d94&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1413592330304356402", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Help with team building", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1413623716419604565", "channel_id": "1413592330304356402", "type": 19, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "The way you play Daffodil is to exalt her and choose her 2 cost. \n\nIt adds the most amount of counter in game.\n\nAfter playing her 2 cost you exalt Nautila.", "timestamp": "2025-09-05T20:35:57.853000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["606955103601295381"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1413615743664390234", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1413592330304356402", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Help with team building", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1413625087155769547", "channel_id": "1413592330304356402", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "„Certain stages“ and „endgame“.\nI think this person wants general advice early on and blue is just objectively the best. \nSo even if ultra would not be the worst realm endgame, then it would still not change the fact that this person is a super new player (lvl 20 units) and can’t even beat the lowest d-Tide rn", "timestamp": "2025-09-05T20:41:24.662000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1413592330304356402", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Help with team building", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
