{"id": "1413638795202531451", "channel_id": "1413592330304356402", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "Doll inferno buffs  Daffodil's ability to add counter.\n\nThis team doesn't need strength building they need ailemus. So Horla and gdoll are there to help them all exalt.\n\nHameln doesn't help other units exalt. He does add to the team in other ways, but ultimately this is an exalt often team and he is better used elsewhere.", "timestamp": "2025-09-05T21:35:52.915000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1413592330304356402", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Help with team building", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
